---
title: French Lentils with Roasted Roots, Walnuts and Cheesy Croutons
description: This French-inspired dish is a delight, bursting with aromatics from tarragon and garlic and the earthy tones of lentils and walnuts. Then there's the warmth of wholegrain mustard, the sweetness of honey and everything gets topped off with crunchy croutons. It's a winner!
